    "title": "关于修订《京东开放平台个人/个体纠纷处理规则》的公示通知",
    "followRuleId": "1255060997891297280",
    "content": "<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 您好，为适应业务发展需求，将修订《京东开放平台个人/个体纠纷处理规则》，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">现进行规则公示，公示期：2025年6月27日- </span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">2025年7月3日，<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000;\">规则预计于2025年7月4日生效，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">公示期满平台将另行发布正式生效规则。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"> </span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">核心调整点：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 微软雅黑, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #f8f8f9; float: none; display: inline;\">订单结算前，如该订单产生的纠纷单未处理完成则该订单延迟结算。待纠纷单处理完成后，对该订单进行结算。</span> </span></span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">原规则链接：<a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1090233093538844672&amp;btype=12\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1090233093538844672&amp;btype=12</a></span></span></span></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; color: #000000;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; white-space-collapse: preserve;\">修订后内容如下：</span></span></span></strong></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.3333px; white-space-collapse: preserve;\"><strong>第三章 附则</strong></span></div>\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; scrollbar-color: auto; scrollbar-width: thin; max-width: 100%; background-color: #ffffff; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13.3333px; white-space-collapse: preserve; color: #e03e2d;\"><strong>第十九条 </strong>对于判定商责的，京东有权而非义务从商家结算款或保证金中直接扣划相应款项退赔给消费者；京东先行垫付退赔款的，若商家结算款或保证金不足以弥补京东先行垫付款项损失的，京东有权从商家关联公司等关联方的结算款或保证金中直接予以扣划。订单结算前，如该订单产生的纠纷单未处理完成则该订单延迟结算。待纠纷单处理完成后，对该订单进行结算。</span></div>",
